KUWAIT CITY, October 18 (Xinhua) -- Hypnotism has become a successful experiment to rid extra fat in obese men and women in Kuwait, a specialist said here today
The number of people coming to clinics for this particular treatment is on the rise
Kuwait has a large percentage of obesity cases among its 700,000 citizens, especially women, because of less activities and unrational food structure
Kuwait has started this medical experiment on obesity cases recently
So far it is the third Arab country that has been using this method after Egypt and Lebanon which have been applying the treatment
